== Description
only create or edit a page in google sites
https://sites.google.com


== Dependencies
gem install mechanize


== Bugs
* There is no error processing.
* the error occurs when the page that already exists is made
* when you create new page, you cant select a template except for "Web page"
* when you edit a page, its page is overwritten


== Examples

=== Set up
set a path, email and password
ex) https://sites.google.com/site/YOUR_SITES/
path = '/site/YOUR_SITES/'
email = ''
password = ''

==== when you use google apps
path = '/a/EXAMPLE.COM/YOUR_SITES/'


=== Log in
gs = GoogleSites.new(path)
gs.login(email, password)


=== Create new page
ex) create hoge page under the example page
[ATTENTION] It is necessary already to make the example page
https://sites.google.com/site/YOUR_SITES/SOURCE_PATH/PATH_NAME

source_path = "example"
path_name = "hoge"
title = "hoge title"
text = "<a href='http://example.com'>Create hoge page</a>"
gs.create(path_name, title, text, source_path)


=== Edit a page(overwrite a page)
ex) edit a hoge page
https://sites.google.com/site/YOUR_SITES/EDIT_PATH

edit_title = "Edit"
edit_text = "<a href='http://example.com'>Edit hoge page</a>"
edit_path = "example/hoge"
gs.edit(edit_title, edit_text, edit_path)
